data.revised_prompt: An illustration of an isolated stop sign. The signpost is firmly planted in the ground and stands out boldly against a sparse background. The stop sign itself is well-defined, with the familiar octagonal shape and bright red color that unmistakably signifies 'stop'. Reflective white letters spell out the word 'STOP' across the center in uppercase. The edges of the sign are slightly worn, hinting at age and regular exposure to the elements.

message.content: The image features a classic stop sign, which is octagonal in shape and bright red in color. The word "STOP" is prominently displayed in bold white letters, drawing attention. The sign has a slightly textured surface, adding depth to its appearance. It is mounted on a simple pole, set against a light, neutral background that highlights the vivid colors of the sign. Overall, the image conveys a clear message, emphasizing the importance of stopping.
